    ./in.cue:7:3
    ./in.cue:7:24
    ./in.cue:9:4
    ./in.cue:10:5
    ./in.cue:58:2
[eval] outB: conflicting values {val:k,if isConcrete(val) {k}} and "b" (mismatched types struct and string):
    ./in.cue:16:7
    ./in.cue:17:2
    ./in.cue:18:3
    ./in.cue:18:25
